  "title": "EasyPinCamera",
  "description": "Control Camera just like C4D",
  "longDescription": "<p><strong>Easy Pin Camera</strong> is a camera control tool designed specifically for Unreal Engine (UE4), inspired by Cinema 4D&#39;s camera operation style. It allows users to achieve precise camera control with simple actions. The core features of the tool include:</p><ul><li><strong>Precise Panning</strong>: Middle mouse button panning ensures that the target point accurately follows the mouse movement.</li><li><strong>Fine-Tune Zooming</strong>: Zoom in with the right mouse button, and hold the Alt key for fine adjustments, catering to various scene needs.</li><li><strong>Flexible Rotation</strong>: Rotate the camera with the left mouse button, allowing it to orbit around a target point, even if the point is not centered in the view, keeping the target&#39;s screen position constant.</li></ul><p><strong>Easy Pin Camera</strong> focuses on a straightforward and intuitive user experience, making it suitable for any scenario requiring high-precision camera control, whether it&#39;s architectural visualization, virtual cinematography, or game development, significantly enhancing your workflow efficiency.</p>",
  "technicalDetails": "<p>Features:</p><p>Number of Blueprints:1</p><p>Input:Keyboard, Mouse</p><p><a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/10co6nUDUKc3Bayaoe6wPxVhxTDRN0FFv/view?usp&#61;sharing\" rel=\"nofollow\">Demo</a></p><p><a href=\"https://pan.baidu.com/s/1MYtYfHcmAsk3Cmhn_YEGOg?pwd&#61;8z7s\" rel=\"nofollow\">Demo(网盘)</a></p>",
